4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists, regardless of their prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and comprises three live online classes each week with a maximum of 18 participants. Students will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while learning advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The bootcamp is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop